title: Asadabad, Khuzestan
content:
Asadabad (Persian: اسداباد, also Romanized as Asadābād)[1] is a village in Dodangeh Rural District, in the Central District of Behbahan County, Khuzestan Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 1,188, in 223 families.[2]
